{
  "stem": "210.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I used to-- we had some people that they used to make socks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they had a little machine at home, and they used to make socks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I would take the socks and go from, you know, to some people that I knew to sell the socks, you know-- gentile people that I knew-- and sell the socks, and, you know, whatever I could.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then, across the street from where my grandfather lived, there was the German church.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was an Evangelical church.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and this was right across from my grandfather's house and bakery-- practically from the bakery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so I went over to her, and I told her that she should give me any kind of work, that I have to help out and-- with the family things like-- my sister is younger.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My brother is younger.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there's nobody to make any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So she gave me a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She gave me a job to work in the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I used to help her with the cooking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember-- I don't remember if they had children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think they had children, because they were so young.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she really was very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And some of the things that we used to have that my father took out from the cellar-- so let's say, one time we sold her the candlesticks.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "One time we sold her, you know, because I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because he was supposed to give it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we-- some things we kept.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So she gave us some money for this, some money for that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Then I helped her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She had like a big garden, a vegetable garden, in the back of the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I used to, you know, help in the gardens.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
